# ===== Firebase =====
# IMPORTANT: Never commit your real google-services.json to a public repo!
# The placeholder in the repo will be detected by the .json content (no "current_key" value)
# Replace app/google-services.json with your actual Firebase config locally.
# In CI/CD, inject it via the GOOGLE_SERVICES_JSON secret (already configured in the workflow).

